      • OntObservation

        public OntObservation(java.lang.String providerService,
                      java.util.List<org.apache.jena.rdf.model.RDFNode> stateValues,
                      java.lang.String timestamp)
        Constructor for creating an ontology observation. It describes a state change regarding to one specific providerService with an timestamp.
        Parameters:
        providerService - is the providerService to identify the kind of state values.
        stateValues - are the values of an state change to a specific time.
        timestamp - is the specific time with the format: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSSXXX.
